Package: Romdb
Title: Retrieve movie information using the OMDb API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Ho", email = "simonsays87@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Request movie information (e.g., year of release, description, rating)
    using the Open Movie Database API (http://omdbapi.com/). Movie information can
    be pulled directly by name, or queried using a search string.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
Imports: httr
URL: https://github.com/sho-87/Romdb
BugReports: https://github.com/sho-87/Romdb/issues
